FirstTimers.Name: macrozheng/mall-swarm
FirstTimers.Description: mall-swarm是一套微服务商城系统，采用了 Spring Cloud Greenwich、Spring Boot 2、MyBatis、Docker、Elasticsearch等核心技术，同时提供了基于Vue的管理后台方便快速搭建系统。mall-swarm在电商业务的基础集成了注册中心、配置中心、监控中心、网关等系统功能。文档齐全，附带全套Spring Cloud教程。

FirstTimers.Name: jagenjo/litegraph.js
FirstTimers.Description: A graph node engine and editor written in Javascript similar to PD or UDK Blueprints, comes with its own editor in HTML5 Canvas2D. The engine can run client side or server side using Node. It allows to export graphs as JSONs to be included in applications independently.
